                <h1>Discover the Evolution of IBM: A Brief History</h1>
                <p>IBM, founded in 1911 as the Computing-Tabulating-Recording Company, evolved into a tech giant known for innovation. Throughout its history, IBM played a pivotal role in mainframe development, personal computing, and AI advancements. Key milestones include the introduction of the IBM PC in 1981 and the Watson AI in 2011.</p>
